Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:21.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}掌上的微风 在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:35.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}我已经能用全新的笑容 向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:47.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}尽管回忆溢满心头 我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:57.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无所谓在干掉的泪痕中 有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:10.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}没错 我会以迎接朋友的方式 温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:23.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头 我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:27.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,五代,给他喝个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧!喝吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点,不要冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后 我跟她的关系变成了什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是两天后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:01:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说,我很惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她居然能如此坦率地 接受我的爱的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说郁子的英文考了92分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么,原来是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该早点告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也拜托你好好教郁子喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她之间的裂痕 也总算修复了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#10 海滩爱情恐慌! 情敌讨厌小狗!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要送去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 那是二丁目的大叶先生要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子真好啊,闲闲没事干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?不要看不起小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子也有小孩子的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会有什么烦恼嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗发精,洗发精…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,忘记带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天碰到你很多次耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在是暑假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好惨喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假作业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说暑假有出去玩的话 要把它写在图画日记里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我妈又是那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸到了假日 也好像很累的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦!你家有爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你这个房客也很少看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这倒是让我想起小时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我也有同样的功课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅行的话 要把那个地方的地图画下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有去旅行的人 就交一篇自由研究
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家是开店的 全家都在店里忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也每天都被叫到店里帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写自由研究的,只有五代耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好惨喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好恨会出这种鬼作业的 那个没大脑的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,现在还有学校 会出这种作业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说,很痛苦的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是家庭不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,我要学坏!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去海边玩?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?你真的要带我去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,妈妈,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说,大哥哥说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个大哥哥啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢的五代哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥说要带我去海边玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧?让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了,贤太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员也一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,你跟去的话 我也比较放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人多比较好玩啊 好啦,去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧,去吧,去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了,太棒了 可以一起去海边玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了,太棒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:06:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个嗜好还真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱着自己的游泳裤 有那么舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚回去!你这个变态!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么变成这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要教郁子游泳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,我在电话跟她说了 她就坚持要跟着来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁子没有关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那家伙叫来的是大婶吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以省下电车费啊 你这个穷学生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,你那么忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里,今天我刚好也很想游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常的日子竟然有时间去海边玩 你还真是闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟上班族不一样 我的时间比较自由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然没有学生那么自由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我也要打工很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,你终于要买脚踏车了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那么奢侈享受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是赚生活费
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还真是罕见,不过很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的时候吃点苦是很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我还很年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输你的 也只有年轻这一项
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻就有可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲 拿看不见的未来当挡箭牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,路上小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢走…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个白痴,大白痴…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子好少喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,照这种速度 大概两个小时就能到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么有狗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是我们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干嘛把它带来?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为惣一郎也想到海边玩水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋,这样已经超载了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能让它下车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗应该不算在人数里面吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要停在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车会累的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸色不太好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是折回去比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,我已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐,请你先回车上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧,我马上就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在这里一决胜负是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:11:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你会开车吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?到底会不会?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只会骑脚踏车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个?你是指狗吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,就是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你怕狗吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候被狗吓过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点都不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我在开车喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下真的事态严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰,你的脸色又发白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎 说不定我马上就会去陪你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着真的太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,开车那么粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛,我还以为死定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是那个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥,走吧走吧 我们去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员也一起来玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到这么弱不禁风…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把狗带走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧,我就仗义相助救你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,惣一郎,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎好像很喜欢三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它真的很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一旦喜欢上一个人 就会一直黏着他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抱着你走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,对不起,很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,一点都不重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这家伙在 他就不能接近管理员了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大好机会,大好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤太郎,你帮我看一下惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理员,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想游到深一点的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一个人不要紧吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我婶婶很会游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不,凡事要预防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有几年没来海边了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然跟我装蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个女孩子太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一碰上色狼就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太大胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道因为我是寡妇的关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我要跟你说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个寡妇没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没打算装什么纯情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是水母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,是水母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 原来刚才那个是水母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 原来你是用那种眼光在看我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…五代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你就一个人慢慢游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是个危险的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以算了 你在生气不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐,要不要上来坐?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种冷漠的男朋友 不要理他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没钓到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还在生气吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闷不吭声地让人觉得好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看起来像一对情侣吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惊人的恢复力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,那是什么啊,好逊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,过来,我们去玩沙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,两位小姐 你们是从哪里来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接球!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.13,0:17:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,三鹰 你的身体没事了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,已经完全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位小姐 我的女伴回来了,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就住在那间饭店里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚请过来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾,我今天就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是容易受女孩子 玩弄的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去划船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去划吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赖皮鬼,居然你们大人自己去划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,我们马上就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好无聊的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来教你如何划船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像蛮好玩的 可是我学得会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你坐到我的旁边来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定马上就能学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么一下子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两手握着划桨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握的方法有点不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,要像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全无视我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桨稍微压低一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,稍微再…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?橡皮艇不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才听见惣一郎的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛? 刚才那个叫声不是我装的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,它要被冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,看我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代 三鹰,拜托你快把船划过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,乖喔乖喔,已经没事了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把惣一郎带到船上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你罗,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事一桩,那我先回去罗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰,接下来就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我…我想去坐橡皮艇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体又不舒服了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太没用了 居然连划个船也会晕船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点回去的话要天黑了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋 我也很担心一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧,我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还是不行的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我来开车吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是意外啊 想不到你有驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我考上驾照以后 从来都没有上路的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得能不能开得好 因为我没办法分心看后视镜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我坐在前座帮忙你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是前座的死亡率最高耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能死在你的手里 我也死而无憾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员请系上安全带!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎,发动!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在跑了耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐,开慢一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.61,0:22:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讲话!我会分心的!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:22:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.09,0:23:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员开车很有男子气概
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超了好多台车
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟郁子都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是五代哥哥和网球教练 却吓得全身发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.93,0:23:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,问大家一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次回想起来 心头都会一阵悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.21,0:23:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种酸酸甜甜的感觉 这是什么回忆呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.21,0:23:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案是初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:23:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.85,0:24:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘贤太郎的初恋! 只要有爱年龄不是问题’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早熟的贤太郎 他的初恋情人究竟是谁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:06.61,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:35.69,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}为何你能如此若无其事
